data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA MORTGAGE AT 4.75%.  APPROXIMATE LOAN BALANCE $196,180, and PITI is $1597.  Wait till you see this stunning, gorgeous home which backs to Founders Park. Enter into the great room with beautiful hardwood floors and wander to your large hearth room kitchen with gas fireplace. Check out the kitchen stainless steel appliances, from 2016, which all stay. Enjoy the hearth room with gas fireplace. Main floor laundry and 1/2 bath complete the first floor. Go up the 2-story staircase with large window & enter into a loft area and the four upstairs bedrooms. Master suite has oversize vanity, soaking tub and shower, 2 walk-ins. Finished LL has a craft room/den with built-ins, a wet bar and a nice family room, plus a full bath with stand-up shower. Other updates: professional 5.1 & 7.1 surround sound wiring on the main floor & downstairs, TV bracket(s) w extension arm that stay, E-Shield energy system installed 2016.
